sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant BalanceDomain as TokenBalance
    participant TransDomain as TokenTransaction
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/admin/tokens/credits
    Note right of Client: {userId, amount: 100000, reason}

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract payload
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create AddTokenCreditsCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(command)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(command)
    Validator->>Validator: Check amount > 0
    Validator->>Validator: Check reason is provided
    Validator->>Validator: Verify admin role
    Validator->>DB: Check user exists
    DB-->>Validator: User found ✓
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Get or create TokenBalance
    DB-->>Handler: TokenBalance

    Handler->>BalanceDomain: balance.AddCredits(amount, reason)
    BalanceDomain->>BalanceDomain: AvailableTokens += amount
    BalanceDomain->>BalanceDomain: TotalAllocated += amount
    BalanceDomain->>BalanceDomain: LastUpdatedAt = UtcNow

    Handler->>TransDomain: TokenTransaction.Create(userId, +amount, operation)
    TransDomain->>TransDomain: Create transaction record

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(balance, transaction)
    DB-->>Handler: Saved ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish TokenCreditsAddedEvent

    Handler-->>Mediator: TokenBalanceDto
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: TokenBalanceDto

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {availableTokens, totalAllocated}
